author: Kyle Hodge
title: Paris Jackson Style Moments Through the Years
text:
Paris Jackson Style Moments Through the Years From "Thiller" inspired looks to Balmain. by Kyle Hodge 3 h ago 
Paris Jackson has been on a roll in 2017. She’s graced the cover of Rolling Stone, sent an A1 clapback to Wendy Williams , landed her first acting role , and recently slayed the Grammys with two flawless outfits and a moving tribute to her late father Michael Jackson . In honor of the fire year Paris is having, take a look back at her most stylish looks throughout the years. 
Watch a rare, behind-the-scenes look at the Michael Jackson’s ’This Is It’ tour rehearsal.
